	abstract = {This report presents an evaluation methodology for proliferation resistance and physical protection (PR\&PP) of Generation IV nuclear energy systems (NESs). For a proposed NES design, the methodology defines a set of challenges, analyzes system response to these challenges, and assesses outcomes. The challenges to the NES are the threats
posed by potential actors (proliferant States or sub-national adversaries). The
